description: (Enterprise Tier Only) Commands to view Build Result Resource.

commands.name: az spring build-service build result list
commands.syntax:
az spring build-service build result list --resource-group
                                          --service
                                          [--build-name]
examples: az spring build-service build result list --build-name my-build --service clitest --resource-group cli

commands.name: az spring build-service build result show
commands.syntax:
az spring build-service build result show --resource-group
                                          --service
                                          [--build-name]
                                          [--name]
examples: az spring build-service build result show --name 2 --build-name my-build --service clitest --resource-group cli
